<p>This information can be used to create a graph and connect the points with a smooth curve.</p>
<p><img alt="Graph showing plotted points negative 1 comma 1 divided by a, 0 comma 1, and 1 comma a." src="https://k12.openstax.org/contents/raise/resources/5f3e61aeb92ea3d5878b1e0be83105565b7555cc" width="500"/></p>
